responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "A2D819E04712560EA64BFBAC21DEBF05", "There is no time to wait. I need an agent to venture into the lair of the Forsaken Blades, the ruins of Nika\'Brae. If reports are true, the lost mage has found this place to base out of. This alone, makes no sense when the Blades have control of the Highwaymen Hills. He must be planning to strike at Lionhold.")
